(2005, 1, '2018-06-27 14:44:38', '2018-06-27 14:44:38', '[vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content_no_spaces\" gap=\"2\" content_placement=\"top\" bg_type=\"image\" parallax_style=\"vcpb-default\" bg_image_new=\"id^1757|url^https://paulwilliselectrical.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/20170602_133847.jpg|caption^null|alt^null|title^20170602_133847|description^null\" bg_image_repeat=\"no-repeat\" bg_override=\"ex-full\" enable_overlay=\"enable_overlay_value\" overlay_pattern=\"01.png\" overlay_pattern_opacity=\"77\" css=\".vc_custom_1527937387737{padding-top: 8% !important;padding-bottom: 8% !important;}\"][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_custom_heading text=\"ABOUT US\" font_container=\"tag:h2|text_align:center|color:%23ffffff\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1527873753136{padding-top: 60px !important;padding-bottom: 25px !important;}\"][vc_column width=\"2/3\" css=\".vc_custom_1527873787870{padding-bottom: 50px !important;}\"][ultimate_heading main_heading=\"Experience\" alignment=\"left\" main_heading_style=\"font-weight:bold;\" main_heading_font_size=\"desktop:26px;\" main_heading_line_height=\"desktop:32px;\" main_heading_margin=\"margin-bottom:20px;\"][/ultimate_heading][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1527878475075{padding-bottom: 40px !important;}\"]At Paul Willis Electrical Ltd, we pride ourselves on providing an electrical service that has served Colne, Burnley, and Barnoldswick for over 20 years.\r\n\r\nWe have covered the same area for over 20 years and throughout that time, our professional service has been recommended by many. We have the experience of working in an industry that has evolved and changed but we always ensure that we adhere to all laws and regulations.\r\n\r\nOur experience guarantees the highest level of workmanship and we always strive to provide our customers with a service they expect. We 