27792901886{padding-top: 40px !important;}\"]Our service stretches beyond that of the domestic sector because we also cover both commercial and industrial. Our ability to provide a service that can adapt to your specific needs is what enables us to stand ahead of our competitors. Whether you have maintenance and repair requirements or you simply want to improve the efficiency of your business, we are on hand to provide you with the advice, guidance, and workmanship that helps our service to stand out.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWe are the experts and we firmly believe that our service will meet your every need. We might be a small, established business but we have highly trained electricians and the experience that enables us to deliver every single job we take on.\r\n\r\nWe are 100% compliant with the full 17<sup>th</sup> Edition BS7671 and all of our work is fully insured and guaranteed.\r\n\r\nWe pay attention to the finer details because that allows us to deliver the high standards that have helped us to excel for more than 20 years.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '363-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-06-07 15:54:31', '2018-06-07 15:54:31', '', 363, 'https://paulwilliselectrical.co.uk/363-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
