 property with the respect they deserve. Our team of friendly and professional experts are on hand to answer any queries you might have and to ensure that all work is completed to a level of quality that delivers complete satisfaction.[/vc_column_text][ultimate_heading main_heading=\"Honesty and Reliability\" alignment=\"left\" main_heading_style=\"font-weight:bold;\" main_heading_font_size=\"desktop:26px;\" main_heading_line_height=\"desktop:32px;\" main_heading_margin=\"margin-bottom:20px;\"][/ultimate_heading][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1527952430670{padding-bottom: 40px !important;}\"]Our domestic electrical service is underpinned by our ability to work in a way that fits your specific needs. From the moment we provide you with a quote, we are here for you. We make our costs and prices as clear as possible and we ensure that our work plans are suitable for you. We always make sure that we work with you and so, we work to deadlines that work for you and we stick the agreed work that is expected of us, as well as the agreed cost.[/vc_column_text][ultimate_heading main_heading=\"Efficiency and Effective\" alignment=\"left\" main_heading_style=\"font-weight:bold;\" main_heading_font_size=\"desktop:26px;\" main_heading_line_height=\"desktop:32px;\" main_heading_margin=\"margin-bottom:20px;\"][/ultimate_heading][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1527952550663{padding-bottom: 40px !important;}\"]From the moment you choose to use our domestic services, we make sure that we work efficiently to complete the job in hand. Our aim is to put your home back to how it was if we are carrying out emergency work or if we are carrying out home improvements, we guarantee an impressive job. We ensure that your work is clean and effective because we appreciate that we are working in your home. Our staff are courteous and considerate and on longer jobs, we clear away our equipment at the end of every day.\r\n\r\nOur domestic service is highly regarded and that is why we come as highly recommended. Our ability to pay attention to detail and look after your needs is what sets us apart from our competitors.\r\n\r\nWe are highly qualified in every aspect of electrical work and so, you can put your trust in us. We pride ourselves on an impeccable service that goes above and beyond to meet your domestic electrical needs. Our service is underpinned by several key aspects: Friendliness, professionalism, honesty and great workmanship. All of these work together to deliver a service that offers so much more than our competitors.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\" css=\".vc_custom_1527873801959{padding-bottom: 50px !important;}\"][vc_column_text]\r\n<h3><span style=\"color: #f96408;\"><strong>The Services we offer</strong></span></h3>\r\n&nbsp;\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Inspection and Testing</li>\r\n 	<li>Rewires</li>\r\n 	<li>Lighting Installations</li>\r\n 	<li>Cooker and Shower Installations</li>\r\n 	<li>LED Upgrades</li>\r\n 	<li>Fuse Board Upgrades</li>\r\n 	<li>Outdoor lighting</li>\r\n 	<li>Kitchen and Bathroom Wiring</li>\r\n 	<li>Socket Installation</li>\r\n 	<li>Emergency Repairs</li>\r\n 	<li>Extensions and Conversions</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_single_image image=\"1884\" img_size=\"large\" alignment=\"center\" image_hovers=\"false\" css=\".vc_custom_1527950851533{padding-top: 30px !important;}\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row][vc_column width=\"2/3\"][ultimate_heading main_heading=\"Quotes and Advice \" alignment=\"left\" main_heading_style=\"font-weight:bold;\" main_heading_font_size=\"desktop:26px;\" main_heading_line_height=\"desktop:32px;\" main_heading_margin=\"margin-bottom:20px;\"][/ultimate_heading][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1527952606687{padding-bottom: 40px !important;}\"]We can provide a free quote that comes with our no-obligation promise. We are also willing to offer free advice and guidance regarding all electrical work or projects. We believe our service is the best in the area and are confident that you will benefit from our knowledge, experience, and workmanship.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content_no_spaces\" content_placement=\"middle\" bg_type=\"bg_color\" bg_color_value=\"#f96408\" css=\".vc_custom_1527949561574{padding-top: 10px !important;}\"][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][bsf-info-box icon=\"icomoon-icomoonfree-16x16-phone\" icon_size=\"32\" icon_color=\"#ffffff\" title=\"Call- 07807769053\" heading_tag=\"h2\"][/bsf-info-box][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Domestic', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '1875-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-06-02 15:32:19', '2018-06-02 15:32:19', '', 1875, 'https://paulwilliselectrical.co.uk/2018/06/02/1875-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
