(1873, 1, '2018-06-02 14:27:59', '2018-06-02 14:27:59', '[vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content_no_spaces\" gap=\"2\" content_placement=\"top\" bg_type=\"image\" parallax_style=\"vcpb-default\" bg_image_new=\"id^1832|url^https://paulwilliselectrical.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2018/06/paul1.jpg|caption^Lighting at hall ceiling.|alt^null|title^Lighting at hall ceiling.|description^null\" bg_image_repeat=\"no-repeat\" bg_override=\"ex-full\" enable_overlay=\"enable_overlay_value\" overlay_pattern=\"01.png\" overlay_pattern_opacity=\"77\" css=\".vc_custom_1527945206925{padding-top: 8% !important;padding-bottom: 8% !important;}\"][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"2/3\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_custom_heading text=\"Commercial and Industrial\" font_container=\"tag:h2|text_align:center|color:%23ffffff\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/6\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1527873753136{padding-top: 60px !important;padding-bottom: 25px !important;}\"][vc_column width=\"2/3\" css=\".vc_custom_1527873787870{padding-bottom: 50px !important;}\"][ultimate_heading main_heading=\"An Expert Electrical Service for your Industrial and Commercial needs\" alignment=\"left\" main_heading_style=\"font-weight:bold;\" main_heading_font_size=\"desktop:26px;\" main_heading_line_height=\"desktop:32px;\" main_heading_margin=\"margin-bottom:20px;\"][/ultimate_heading][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1527945286587{padding-bottom: 40px !important;}\"]At Paul Willis Electrical Ltd, we understand that operating a business efficiently, is key to its success. Therefore, we appreciate just how important it is to have electrical experts on hand to assist you when required. Our service covers Colne, Burnley, and Barnoldswick and is here to meet all of your Industrial and Commercial needs. Throughout our 20 years of working in this industry, we have worked with many businesses and delivered a high standard of workmanship, every single time.\r\n\r\nOur ability to work around your specific needs ensures that we do not disrupt your business operations while ensuring we deliver work of the highest quality. We work professionally, efficiently and always ensure we are on hand to work with you and your requirements.[/vc_column_text][ultimate_heading main_heading=\"Our Services\" alignment=\"left\" main_heading_style=\"font-weight:bold;\" main_heading_font_size=\"desktop:26px;\" main_heading_line_height=\"desktop:32px;\" main_heading_margin=\"margin-bottom:20px;\"][/ultimate_heading][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1527945362298{padding-bottom: 40px !important;}\"]We offer a comprehensive range of Commercial and Industrial Electrical service to businesses throughout the area. Therefore, we can design and install new electrical systems and maintain existing installations.\r\n\r\nWe have an extensive knowledge and experience of the relevant Health and Safety legislation within this sector and so, we can help you meet your obligations. Over the last 20 years, we have seen the commercial and industrial sectors change considerably. The number of Health and Safety regulations have grown, with many requiring businesses to enhance performance, cut costs and look at ways or reducing energy usage and waste. Therefore, we can help in all areas.[/vc_column_text][info_list style=\"hexagon\" icon_bg_color=\"#f96408\" icon_color=\"\" font_size_icon=\"24\" eg_br_width=\"1\"][info_list_item list_title=\"MAINTENANCE AND REPAIRS\" list_icon=\"Defaults-wrench\"]Whether you require a new electrical installation or requires us to carry out repairs and maintenance on an old system, we are here for you. We have a team of knowledgeable experts who have the qualifications and skills to undertake all repair and regular maintenance work.[/info_list_item][info_list_item list_title=\"ENHANCED EFFICIENCY AND REDUCED ENERGY USE\" list_icon=\"icomoon-icomoonfree-16x16-sort-amount-desc\"]We appreciate that all businesses are now 