(1823, 1, '2018-06-02 11:03:04', '2018-06-02 11:03:04', '[vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row_content_no_spaces\" gap=\"2\" content_placement=\"top\" bg_type=\"image\" parallax_style=\"vcpb-default\" bg_image_new=\"id^1757|url^https://paulwilliselectrical.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/20170602_133847.jpg|caption^null|alt^null|title^20170602_133847|description^null\" bg_image_repeat=\"no-repeat\" bg_override=\"ex-full\" enable_overlay=\"enable_overlay_value\" overlay_pattern=\"01.png\" overlay_pattern_opacity=\"77\" css=\".vc_custom_1527937387737{padding-top: 8% !important;padding-bottom: 8% !important;}\"][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner][vc_custom_heading text=\"ABOUT US\" font_container=\"tag:h2|text_align:center|color:%23ffffff\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1527873753136{padding-top: 60px !important;padding-bottom: 25px !important;}\"][vc_column width=\"2/3\" css=\".vc_custom_1527873787870{padding-bottom: 50px !important;}\"][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1527878460084{padding-bottom: 40px !important;}\"]At Paul Willis Electrical Ltd, we pride ourselves on providing an electrical service that has served Colne, Burnley, and Barnoldswick for over 20 years.\r\n\r\nThroughout the years, we have evolved and grown into the company that we are today. It has taken dedication, hard work, and commitment, but we take great pride from delivering complete customer satisfaction.\r\n\r\nWe have always aimed to offer the best service at a cost that cannot be beaten and that is why we lead from the front. Through creating a high level of customer satisfaction and providing a service that exceeds expectations, we have a wide client base, many of which return to us. Our reputation goes before us and that is what creates a level of trust and reliability that speaks volumes.[/vc_column_text][ultimate_heading main_heading=\"Experience\" alignment=\"left\" main_heading_style=\"font-weight:bold;\" main_heading_font_size=\"desktop:26px;\" main_heading_line_height=\"desktop:32px;\" main_heading_margin=\"margin-bottom:20px;\"][/ultimate_heading][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1527878475075{padding-bottom: 40px !important;}\"]At Paul Willis Electrical Ltd, we pride ourselves on providing an electrical service that has served Colne, Burnley, and Barnoldswick for over 20 years.\r\n\r\nWe have covered the same area for over 20 years and throughout that time, our professional service has been recommended by many. We have the experience of working in an industry that has evolved and changed but we always ensure that we adhere to all laws and regulations.\r\n\r\nOur experience guarantees the highest level of workmanship and we always strive to provide our customers with a service they expect. We pay attention to the smallest of details while taking care of the job in hand.[/vc_column_text][ultimate_heading main_heading=\"Our Services\" alignment=\"left\" main_heading_style=\"font-weight:bold;\" main_heading_font_size=\"desktop:26px;\" main_heading_line_height=\"desktop:32px;\" main_heading_margin=\"margin-bottom:20px;\"][/ultimate_heading][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1527878485661{padding-bottom: 40px !important;}\"]We cover both the domestic and Industrial &amp; Commercial Sectors.\r\n\r\nOur experienced, highly skilled and technical team of experts have the ability to work on a wide range of jobs, regardless of the sector. You might be a homeowner who needs additional sockets fitting or a business owner who requires the installation of emergency lighting, therefore, we cover the following:[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1527880351204{padding-bottom: 40px !important;}\"]\r\n<h4><span style=\"color: #f96408;\"><strong>Domestic Service:</strong></span></h4>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>Sockets &amp; Light Fitting installations</li>\r\n 	<li>Fuse board upgrades</li>\r\n 	<li>LED spotlights</li>\r\n 	<li>Fault Finding</li>\r\n 	<li>Shower Installations</li>\r\n 	<li>Cooker InstallationsSmoke &amp; CO2 Alarm Installations</li>\r\n 	<li>Security Alarm &amp; Lighting systems</li>\r\n 	<li>Heating Controls including Smart systems eg: Nest &amp; Hive</li>\r\n 	<li>Electrical Testing &amp; Inspection (EICR)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1527880486596{padding-bottom: 40px !important;}\"]<span style=\"color: #f96408;\"><strong>Industrial and Commercial Service:</strong></span>\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>All Single or 3 Phase installations</li>\r\n 	<li>Shop renovations</li>\r\n 	<li>LED lighting upgrades</li>\r\n 	<li>Emergency Lighting</li>\r\n 	<li>Maintenance contracts</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/vc_column_text][ultimate_heading main_heading=\"Our work is Guaranteed\" alignment=\"left\" main_heading_style=\"font-weight:bold;\" main_heading_font_size=\"desktop:26px;\" main_heading_line_height=\"desktop:32px;\" main_heading_margin=\"margin-bottom:20px;\"][/ultimate_heading][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1527880730587{padding-bottom: 40px !important;}\"]All of our work comes fully insured, providing you with complete peace of mind. We also guarantee that our workmanship will fulfil your every need. We complete every job to the highest of standards and so, we are here for you until we achieve complete satisfaction.[/vc_column_text][ultimate_heading main_heading=\"We are here for you\" alignment=\"left\" main_heading_style=\"font-weight:bold;\" main_heading_font_size=\"desktop:26px;\" main_heading_line_height=\"desktop:32px;\" main_heading_margin=\"margin-bottom:20px;\"][/ultimate_heading][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1527882951026{padding-bottom: 40px !important;}\"]We are your friendly and professional local electrician and so, when you need us, just give us a call. We cover all aspects of electrical work ranging from emergency call outs to project work. Whatever your requirements, give us a call today – we can provide a no-obligation quote that will not be beaten![/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/3\" css=\".vc_custom_1527873801959{padding-bottom: 50px !important;}\"][ultimate_heading main_heading=\"A service you can trust\" alignment=\"left\" main_heading_style=\"font-weight:bold;\" main_heading_font_size=\"desktop:26px;\" main_heading_line_height=\"desktop:32px;\" main_heading_margin=\"margin-bottom:20px;\"][/ultimate_heading][vc_single_image image=\"1800\" alignment=\"center\" style=\"vc_box_shadow_3d\"][vc_column_text]There are many Electrical services out there that promise so much but fail to deliver. At Paul Willis Electrical Ltd, we can guarantee that we will go above and beyond to meet your needs. Regardless of the size of the job, we have a team of highly skilled electrical specialists on hand to complete the job in hand. We work with complete professionalism and believe that our service should be honest and transparent. Therefore, we work closely with you to provide you with feedback and progress of all jobs. This keeps you informed and helps you to make the right decisions at every stage.\r\n\r\nWe are proud to be a member of <span style=\"color: #ff0000;\">(insert accreditations, awards or memberships)</span> and all work we undertake is inspected annually to ensure complete compliance and quality. This provides you with a service that consists of the highest standards and ensures that our workmanship continues to improve. We are constantly improving our working methods and always ensure that our understanding of regulations remains up to date.[/vc_column_text][vc_single_image image=\"1759\" img_size=\"large\" alignment=\"center\" image_hovers=\"false\" css=\".vc_custom_1527880621077{padding-top: 30px !important;}\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row content_placement=\"middle\" bg_type=\"bg_color\" bg_override=\"ex-full\" type=\"vc_default\" margin_top=\"-50\" css=\".vc_custom_1527882865157{padding-top: 30px !important;}\" bg_color_value=\"#f96408\"][vc_column width=\"1/4\"][/vc_column]