sktop:20px;\" title_font_line_height=\"desktop:30px;\"]We are your friendly and professional local electrician and so, when you need us, just give us a call.[/bsf-info-box][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\" offset=\"vc_col-lg-3 vc_col-md-3\" css=\".vc_custom_1495112577073{padding-bottom: 50px !important;}\"][bsf-info-box icon=\"Defaults-check\" icon_size=\"32\" icon_color=\"#ffffff\" icon_style=\"circle\" icon_color_bg=\"\" title=\"A SERVICE YOU CAN TRUST\" pos=\"top\" el_class=\"accent-icon-bg\" css_info_box=\".vc_custom_1527867166194{margin-bottom: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 20px !important;}\" title_font_size=\"desktop:20px;\" title_font_line_height=\"desktop:30px;\"]We work with complete professionalism and believe that our service should be honest and transparent.[/bsf-info-box][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row equal_height=\"yes\" content_placement=\"middle\" bg_type=\"bg_color\" bg_override=\"ex-full\" type=\"vc_default\" css=\".vc_custom_1527800528751{padding-top: 50px !important;padding-bottom: 50px !important;}\" bg_color_value=\"rgba(170,170,170,0.1)\"][vc_column][ultimate_heading main_heading=\"Over 20 Years Experience\" spacer=\"line_only\" spacer_position=\"middle\" line_height=\"5\" line_color=\"\" main_heading_font_size=\"desktop:40px;\" main_heading_line_height=\"desktop:46px;\" line_width=\"200\" main_heading_margin=\"margin-bottom:15px;\" main_heading_style=\"font-weight:bold;\" el_class=\"accent-border-color\" margin_design_tab_text=\"\"][/ultimate_heading][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1528386650605{padding-top: 30px !important;}\"]We believe that experience counts for a lot in our industry. We have more than 20 years experience of serving the area, ensuring that our service has evolved throughout this time to meet the ever-changing demands of our clients. We have covered a wide range of jobs from small domestic jobs right through to large commercial jobs. Our ability to call on our experience helps us to meet the requirements of every single job.\r\n\r\nIf you want a service that comes with the right experience, we are here for you.\r\n\r\n.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row bg_type=\"image\" parallax_style=\"vcpb-default\" bg_image_new=\"id^1759|url^https://paulwilliselectrical.co.uk/wp-content/uploads/2018/05/20151103_172920.jpg|caption^null|alt^null|title^20151103_172920|description^null\" bg_override=\"ex-full\" enable_overlay=\"enable_overlay_value\" overlay_color=\"rgba(0,0,0,0.69)\" overlay_pattern=\"07.png\" type=\"vc_default\" css=\".vc_custom_1527849964719{padding-top: 60px !important;padding-bottom: 70px !important;}\"][vc_column][ultimate_heading main_heading=\"\'NEED A LOCAL ELECTRICIAN?\" sub_heading_color=\"#ffffff\" main_heading_font_size=\"desktop:40px;tablet_portrait:20px;\" main_heading_line_height=\"desktop:46px;tablet_portrait:26px;\" main_heading_style=\"font-weight:700;\" main_heading_font_family=\"font_family:Open Sans Condensed|font_call:Open+Sans+Condensed|variant:700\" sub_heading_font_family=\"font_family:Open Sans Condensed|font_call:Open+Sans+Condensed|variant:700\" sub_heading_style=\"font-weight:700;\" sub_heading_font_size=\"desktop:70px;tablet_portrait:40px;\" sub_heading_line_height=\"desktop:76px;tablet_portrait:46px;\" main_heading_margin=\"margin-bottom:10px;\" el_class=\"accent-title-color\" margin_design_tab_text=\"\"]CONTACT US TODAY[/ultimate_heading][dt_default_button link=\"url:%2Fcorporate%2Fcontact|||\" size=\"big\" btn_width=\"btn_fixed_width\" custom_btn_width=\"400\" button_alignment=\"btn_center\" css=\".vc_custom_1528386766350{margin-top: 27px !important;}\"]REQUEST A QUOTE[/dt_default_button][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_id=\"domestic\" css=\".vc_custom_1527792393362{padding-top: 40px !important;padding-bottom: 40px !important;}\"][vc_column css=\".vc_custom_1527787574488{padding-bottom: 50px !important;}\"][vc_row_inner css=\".vc_custom_1527792424740{padding-top: 40px !important;}\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][ultimate_heading main_heading=\"DOMESTIC SERVICES\" spacer=\"line_only\" spacer_position=\"middle\" line_height=\"5\" line_color=\"\" main_heading_font_size=\"desktop:40px;\" main_heading_line_height=\"desktop:46px;\" line_width=\"200\" main_heading_margin=\"margin-bottom:15px;\" main_heading_style=\"font-weight:bold;\" el_class=\"accent-border-color\"][/ultimate_heading][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1527801615986{padding-top: 40px !important;padding-bottom: 15px !important;}\"]Our ability to take on a wide range of electrical jobs makes us the perfect choice for all of your domestic electrical needs. Whether you require a complete re-wire of your home, a light installation or a fuse board upgrade, you can rely on our service. Our team of highly trained electricians is available to assist you with all of your requirements, regardless of whether it is an emergency or a routine job. Our domestic service has been used by many and we are proud of the fact that so many of our clients recommend to us to friends and family.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"1757\" img_size=\"full\" image_hovers=\"false\"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner css=\".vc_custom_1527801584394{padding-top: 30px !important;}\"][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\" css=\".vc_custom_1527803822485{padding-top: 20px !important;}\"][vc_single_image image=\"1755\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"right\" image_hovers=\"false\" css=\".vc_custom_1527803926608{padding-top: 20px !important;}\"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width=\"1/2\"][ultimate_heading main_heading=\"Industrial &amp; Commercial Services\" spacer=\"line_only\" spacer_position=\"middle\" line_height=\"5\" line_color=\"\" main_heading_font_size=\"desktop:40px;\" main_heading_line_height=\"desktop:46px;\" line_width=\"200\" main_heading_margin=\"margin-bottom:15px;\" main_heading_style=\"font-weight:bold;\" el_class=\"accent-border-color\"][/ultimate_heading][vc_column_text css=\".vc_custom_1527792901886{padding-top: 40px !important;}\"]Our service stretches beyond that of the domestic sector because we also cover both commercial and industrial. Our ability to provide a service that can adapt to your specific needs is what enables us to stand ahead of our competitors. Whether you have maintenance and repair requirements or you simply want to improve the efficiency of your business, we are on hand to provide you with the advice, guidance, and workmanship that helps our service to stand out.\r\n\r\n&nbsp;\r\n\r\nWe are the experts and we firmly believe that our service will meet your every need. We might be a small, established business but we have highly trained electricians and the experience that enables us to deliver every single job we take on.\r\n\r\nWe are 100% compliant with the full 17<sup>th</sup> Edition BS7671 and all of our work is fully insured and guaranteed.\r\n\r\nWe pay attention to the finer details because that allows us to deliver the high standards that have helped us to excel for more than 20 years.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Home', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '363-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-06-07 15:52:42', '2018-06-07 15:52:42', '', 363, 'https://paulwilliselectrical.co.uk/363-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
